  "title": "Finance & Controlling Manager (Manufacturing, SFRS, SAP)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Oversee accounting, controlling, management reporting, budgeting, forecasting, and mid-term planning.</li><li>Manage ERP-based financial and controlling processes; prepare and present monthly, quarterly, and annual reports.</li><li>Ensure liquidity management, cash flow monitoring, and act as main liaison with banks and insurers.</li><li>Ensure statutory reporting, tax compliance, and transfer pricing alignment.</li><li>Maintain robust internal controls and support internal/external audits.</li><li>Support investment evaluation, credit risk assessment, and ad-hoc financial analysis.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>ACCA or equivalent</li><li>At least 5 years’ relevant <strong>finance, accounting, and controlling experience</strong> in<strong> Manufacturing/Engineering industries.</strong></li><li>Strong SFRS and Singapore tax knowledge and proficient in SAP.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br />Registration: R1326740</p>",
